page.title: 01LAND COVER AND AMENITIES
page.content: THE PRIMARY LAND COVER ON HAYLING IS OPEN SPACE,CATEGORY 08.THE SECONDARY LAND COVER IS SEA,CATEGORY 20.THE TERTIARY LAND COVER IS RESIDENTIAL, CATEGORY 01.DAW LANE,WEST LANE,FERRY ROAD AND NORTH SHORE ROAD ARE MAINLY SURROUNDED BY FARMLAND CATEGORY 10,11 AND 12.MANOR ROAD AND SINAH LANE ARE MAINLY RESIDENTIAL,CATEGORY 01.IN OUR SQUARE WE HAVE THE FOLLOWING: TWO CHURCHES,TWO BANKS,TWO POSTOFFICES ,TWO GARAGES,TWO HARDWARE SHOPS,TWO FISH AND CHIPS SHOPS,TWO ANTIQUE SHOPS,TWO HAIR SALONS,TWO HOTELS,ONE NEWS AGENT,TWO RESTAURANT,TWO GROCERS,ONE LAUNDRETTE AND ONE BUCHER.
